---
// Value proposition section - "Only mock what you don't control"
---

<section class="py-24 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        Only mock what you don't control
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Scenarist acts as a precision scalpel. It slices off external dependencies while leaving your application logic perfectly intact.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
      <!-- Your Application Card (2/3 width) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-200 dark:border-emerald-500/20 bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-500/5 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-emerald-500"></div>
        <div class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 font-bold">Your Application</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Executes For Real</h3>

        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-[#0A0A0C] border border-emerald-100 dark:border-white/10 rounded text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium shadow-sm">
            Server Components
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-[#0A0A0C] border border-emerald-100 dark:border-white/10 rounded text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium shadow-sm">
            Middleware
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-[#0A0A0C] border border-emerald-100 dark:border-white/10 rounded text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium shadow-sm">
            Zod Validation
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-[#0A0A0C] border border-emerald-100 dark:border-white/10 rounded text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium shadow-sm">
            Session Cookies
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- The Edge Card (1/3 width) -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-500/20 bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-500/5 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-purple-500"></div>
        <div class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 font-bold">The Edge</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Mocked by Scenarist</h3>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 items-center">
          <div class="px-4 py-2 w-full bg-white dark:bg-[#0A0A0C] border border-dashed border-purple-300 dark:border-purple-500/30 rounded text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            Stripe API
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 py-2 w-full bg-white dark:bg-[#0A0A0C] border border-dashed border-purple-300 dark:border-purple-500/30 rounded text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            Auth0
          </div>
          <div class="px-4 py-2 w-full bg-white dark:bg-[#0A0A0C] border border-dashed border-purple-300 dark:border-purple-500/30 rounded text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            SendGrid
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
